    {
      "id": "quote:66da6d012bb305a9",
      "properties": {
        "char_end": 141,
        "char_start": 13,
        "episode_id": "32b9679a-1a2d-5cce-b673-b489694ef798",
        "speaker_id": "person:speaker-01",
        "text": "Welcome back to The Long View. I'm joined by Skanda Amarnath, who reads the macroeconomy for a living. Skanda, good to have you.",
        "timestamp_end_ms": 6000,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 0,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/p07_e04.txt"
      },
      "type": "Quote"
    },
    {
      "id": "person:speaker-02",
      "properties": {
        "name": "Skanda Amarnath"
      },
      "type": "Person"
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:3612d89c17b0c2ec",
      "properties": {
        "char_end": 172,
        "char_start": 159,
        "episode_id": "32b9679a-1a2d-5cce-b673-b489694ef798",
        "speaker_id": "person:speaker-02",
        "text": "Thanks, Alex.",
        "timestamp_end_ms": 12000,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 6000,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/p07_e04.txt"
      },
      "type": "Quote"
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:60d3f3f06f703039",
      "properties": {
        "char_end": 318,
        "char_start": 186,
        "episode_id": "32b9679a-1a2d-5cce-b673-b489694ef798",
        "speaker_id": "person:speaker-01",
        "text": "Today's episode is sponsored by Bloomberg. Bloomberg Terminal is the data spine institutional desks run on. Try bloomberg.com today.",
        "timestamp_end_ms": 18000,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 12000,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/p07_e04.txt"
      },
      "type": "Quote"
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:70e2fb8a138bd5e6",
      "properties": {
        "char_end": 369,
        "char_start": 318,
        "episode_id": "32b9679a-1a2d-5cce-b673-b489694ef798",
        "speaker_id": "person:speaker-01",
        "text": "You describe macro as risk management. Unpack that.",
        "timestamp_end_ms": 24000,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 18000,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/p07_e04.txt"
      },
      "type": "Quote"
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:0bd8a63391d40d60",
      "properties": {
        "char_end": 592,
        "char_start": 387,
        "episode_id": "32b9679a-1a2d-5cce-b673-b489694ef798",
        "speaker_id": "person:speaker-02",
        "text": "Macro is risk management at scale. The job is mostly not being on the wrong side of a regime change \u2014 and the regime change you can name in advance is the one you can position for. The rest is just hoping.",
        "timestamp_end_ms": 30000,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 24000,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/p07_e04.txt"
      },
      "type": "Quote"
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:92fbb6f381c6f29d",
      "properties": {
        "char_end": 798,
        "char_start": 592,
        "episode_id": "32b9679a-1a2d-5cce-b673-b489694ef798",
        "speaker_id": "person:speaker-02",
        "text": "And the economy is a system, not a set of levers. Pull one and three others move. When we back-tested the calls, the misses were always someone treating a correlated system as if the parts were independent.",
        "timestamp_end_ms": 36000,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 30000,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/p07_e04.txt"
      },
      "type": "Quote"
    }
  ],
